article_title: New owners keep Concord Bowl rolling in Iroquois
article_text:
Kankakee, IL (60901)

Today

A mix of clouds and sun. A stray shower or thunderstorm is possible. High 84F. Winds SSW at 10 to 20 mph..

Tonight

A few clouds. A stray shower or thunderstorm is possible. Low around 60F. Winds S at 5 to 10 mph.

article_metadata.author: Robert Themerrthemer@daily-journal.com815-937-3369

og.description: The new owners, David and Rhonda Winters, also from Indiana. They took over the 10-lane Concord last year from Ron and Diana Runkle, who had operated it for 37 years.
